        <abstract> 
<p>Will send copy of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Comments on JC-B’s MS on expression among insane. Asks about weeping in insane men. Do idiots laugh when pleased?</p>
            <p>Thanks for photographs of insane. Asks for additional photographs.</p> 
<p>Comments on Henry Maudsley [<hi rend="italic">Body and mind</hi> (1870)].</p> 
            <p>Pointed ears in the insane.</p>
        </abstract>
